<br>
The only time a Paladin with KEI is liable to go oom is if they are casting significantly more than 2 stuns per mob or if they're using their mana for other things, such as heals.<br>
<br>
This mana thing you claim is such a restriction, isn't much of a restriction at all. <p>The Man in Black: We are men of action, lies do not become us. <br>
