Ok. If you wanna play scenario, I'm game. Same scenario, low 60s group with a lvl 62 warrior or lvl 62 paladin/SK in equal gear. Let's say you're fighting in desert though. Mob pulled, goes to camp. Shaman attempts to slow. But, oh @#%$, he resists (this happends VERY often in desert. I won't take a shaman under lvl 63, or a chanter under 64 if ever doing desert). Slow gets resisted, guess who that mob is going after. Give you three guesses, and warrior is NOT one of them. That mob is ping-ponging over to the slower (or failed slower). <br>
